# LogSignalMesh - Log Frequency & Pattern Analyzer

LogSignalMesh provides burst detection and pattern repetition analysis for system logs or application output.

## Features
- Heatmap-style cluster summary  
- Keyword alerts  
- CLI output  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/24_LogSignalMesh.git
cd 24_LogSignalMesh
python analyze.py
